                  </span></div><br><div class="comment">
                  <span class="commtext c00">Related tangent - I&#x27;d love to see more games (whether or not explicitly &quot;educational&quot;) that are more collaborative and less focused on violence. I remember playing GTA and enjoying its then-new (to me, at least) open-world dynamics and imagining a more peaceful version or mode where you&#x27;d play the role of an EMT or field surgeon, running around helping people and saving lives or something.</span>
