                  <span class="commtext c00">I don&#x27;t believe at all in gamification in education. The kick that inspires new scientists and engineers comes from the gratification of learning or figuring out something as nothing feels better than figuring out how&#x2F;why something is happening and how to push it to it&#x27;s edge cases. Even chasing grades is a perverse incentive IMHO.</span>
