                  <span class="commtext c00">I&#x27;m not seeing a more fundamental issue in this thread; What are we trying to teach, and why? It&#x27;s easy to subject people to studying math, history, etc. What if we wanted to teach appropriate social interaction? Moral analysis (NOT morals)? Critical thinking? Developing self knowledge?<p>The problem is that we need interactions with live humans to explore these subjects. Gaming in the metaverse won&#x27;t do the job.</span>
