                  <span class="commtext c00">I&#x27;m doing this for a customer right now!<p>Using Textract from Amazon to do the OCR. I dump the raw json in a SQLite database.<p>Information extraction is trickier. I extract useful things like lines and pages, locations of lines, set up various columns and now can search the SQLite db either with python code or SQL queries.<p>There&#x27;s of course cost for running textract OCR on AWS. There are open source solutions like Tesseract</span>
